## Third-Party Services

This software integrates with the following third-party services, which have their own terms of service:

### Yelp Fusion API
- Terms of Service: https://www.yelp.com/developers/api_terms
- Privacy Policy: https://www.yelp.com/tos/privacy_policy
- API Documentation: https://docs.developer.yelp.com/

### OpenStreetMap Nominatim API
- Usage Policy: https://operations.osmfoundation.org/policies/nominatim/
- License: Open Database License (ODbL)
- Attribution: © OpenStreetMap contributors

### OpenAI API (Optional)
- Terms of Use: https://openai.com/policies/terms-of-use
- Privacy Policy: https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy
- API Documentation: https://platform.openai.com/docs

## Attribution Requirements

When using this software, please ensure compliance with:

1. **Yelp Attribution**: Display Yelp logo and attribution as required by Yelp API Terms
2. **OpenStreetMap Attribution**: Include "© OpenStreetMap contributors" when using location data
3. **OpenAI Attribution**: Follow OpenAI's usage policies if using AI recommendations

## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational and demonstration purposes. Users are responsible for:
- Obtaining their own API keys from Yelp, OpenAI, and other services
- Complying with all third-party terms of service
- Ensuring proper data handling and privacy compliance
- Rate limiting and responsible API usage

## Data Privacy

This software:
- Stores user data in-memory by default (data is lost on restart)
- Can be configured to use PostgreSQL for persistent storage
- Does not collect or transmit user data to third parties beyond the integrated APIs
- Requires users to review and comply with GDPR, CCPA, and other privacy regulations

